Text:
Quality is good...but stuck at 98.1%. vlc will play the movie, even though it stalls a few times throughout...be patient it will play through the stall points in just a couple of seconds each. The entire movie will play completely through to the end and is very watchable...sort of a new concept even though predictable. The acting was par with Julia as the standout. Hard coded english subs very readable. Someone needs to seed to 100% though. I would give:
V=9
A=9
M=6-7
Thanks for the upload.
